Type: Project
Title: Recipient Plasma Metabolomics as a Predictor of Heart Transplant Severe Primary Graft Dysfunction
Authors@R: person("Joshua", "Preston", email = "joshua.preston@emory.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9834-3017"))
Description: Analysis pipeline for preoperative primary graft dysfunction metabolomics study. 
    This project contains all code and analysis scripts for reproducing the results 
    in Preston et al. 2025, American Journal of Transplantation. 
    Reproducible computational environment available via Docker Hub 
    (jdpreston30/pgd-preop-metabolomics) and archived at Zenodo (see manuscript for DOI).
URL: https://github.com/jdpreston30/PGD-preop-metabolomics, https://hub.docker.com/r/jdpreston30/pgd-preop-metabolomics, https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.17875844
